{
  "stem": "27390.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And not a sound came from the people that were on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was so quiet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we knew we were going to be deported.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know exactly where they're taking us, but we knew that we were going to be deported.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they told us they're taking us for work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we realized they're not taking little children and old people for work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we-- this came to us as a shock, because we didn't-- we didn't-- we and my-- the four us-- of us didn't expect this, because we were all working.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we thought we were safe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, we were taken into this-- we were passing this market, after we passed this scene we saw.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all the-- the streets were-- the SS were running around on their motorbikes, up and down, looking for people, where they was-- [SOB] they could get hold of.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There weren't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Officially, there was nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody was allowed to walk in the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We came to this place of assembly, which was-- before the war, it was a hospital, an isolation hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It had a very big wall, a high wall, surrounded with-- with barbed-wire and glass on top of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It hard-- people shouldn't be able to escape from it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because there were-- it was a sort of a lunatic asylum, there, or people that had infectious diseases.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were taken into this hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the screams and the shouting that was going-- coming out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It had-- it had big-- a big area outside the hospital, with trees and bushes, gardens there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was-- in the center was a big building, where the actual hospital was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we knew, once we get-- they get us into this building, we've had it.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
